snippet.title: Fallout 76 - Season 16: Duel with the Devil
snippet.description:
Fear not! In Season 16, the astoundingly awesome Rip Daring is duking it out with the Jersey Devil. No one *but* the burly hero--*and* Nurse Guinevere *and* Percival--could stand toe to toe with the fearsome cryptid stalking New Jersey. Except you, Vault Dweller.

The hunt begins March 26.
